description = "A stout woman in her sixties with silver-streaked hair bound in practical braids and hands roughened by decades of farm work. As Millbrook's elder, she has guided her village through floods, droughts, and now the bandit menace that threatens to strangle their livelihood. Her eyes hold the weariness of leadership, but also an iron determination to protect her people."
